file_content.text: Gambo's gone now. I don't want any trouble!
You beat Gambo. You maybe need a good lookout?
I need to talk to Gambo.
Gambo doesn't like to be bothered. Republic security keeps bothering him.
Gambo's getting angry. He tells me leave him alone, or I get thumped. I'm not getting thumped for you.
I can handle Gambo. He won't hurt you.
Don't worry.
Okay. But I think we both get thumped.
What a baby.
Not good to make fun of me. I tell Gambo who to crush. I think I want you crushed.
I'll do worse.
All right, all right--I'll get Gambo. Don't blame me if you get thumped.
Said they had to see you, boss. Might have been talking to Republic security.
Republic security already sent someone. I broke her. I'll break you, too.
You don't want to fight me. You want to turn yourself in.
[Force Persuade] Not today.
I don't want to fight you. I gotta go turn myself in.
Gambo! Wait! That's a dirty trick, Jedi.
You've got the attention of Havoc Squad now. It can only get worse from here.
Can't run forever.
Maybe listen, boss. You don't want the Republic Army after you.
Yeah, all right. I'll go talk to the police. Republic can't hold me long anyway.
Sometimes you have to bend the law. But you beat a Republic security officer.
You're in too deep.
Maybe should have killed her, boss. No witnesses.
Shut up, Zooki. Too much heat already. I surrender, maybe I get off easy. We'll see.
You've beaten enough people, Gambo. You're coming with me.
You're under arrest.
Tell Republic security my fists are tired. If you live.
Be reasonable.
Too late now, stranger. Should have run when Zooki said.
You don't want to try.
Ha! This one's funny, Zooki. Good find.
I speak for big, important people. Go bother someone small.
